Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.210 --> 00:00:04.040
This is an expression,
it does not have an equal sign.

00:00:04.040 --> 00:00:07.460
This is an equation because
it does have an equal sign.

00:00:07.460 --> 00:00:10.500
This is an expression and
this is an equation.

00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:14.709
Remember equations have equal signs and
expressions do not.

00:00:14.709 --> 00:00:17.604
It is important to remember
the difference between expressions and

00:00:17.604 --> 00:00:19.070
equations.

00:00:19.070 --> 00:00:21.540
Only equations can be solved.

00:00:21.540 --> 00:00:25.984
In other words, to find a value for
a variable you must have an equal sign.

